OL,2,MKilling the astrophysical chameleon
OL,4,CBryony Lanigan
OL,5,CSun 10:30-11:00
OL,6,CStage C
OL,8,GAstronomical observations show that
OL,9,Gour universe is expanding faster and
OL,10,Gfaster in all directions due to
OL,11,Gsomething we call ‘dark energy’ – but
OL,12,Gwhat exactly is it? There are many
OL,13,Gtheories out there, and
OL,14,Gastrophysicists have an unlikely ally
OL,15,Gin the search – atomic physicists like
OL,16,Gmyself. As part of my PhD research, I
OL,17,Gused lasers to trap and cool atoms to
OL,18,Guse as tiny sensors to search for new
OL,19,Gphysics, including searching for
OL,20,Gevidence of a specific dark energy
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
